# 01 - ISMS Scope

## Purpose

The purpose of this document is to define the scope of the Information Security Management System (ISMS) for the Atlanta Falcons ISO 27001:2022 Risk Assessment Case Study.

## Organization

Atlanta Falcons (Case Study)

Industry: Professional Sports & Entertainment

## Scope Statement

The ISMS applies to information assets, personnel, business processes, and technology systems supporting:

* Ticket Sales Operations
* Fan Engagement Services
* Marketing Operations
* Human Resources
* Finance
* Vendor Management
* Corporate IT Services

## Included Assets

* Microsoft 365
* SharePoint
* Employee Laptops
* Ticketing Systems
* CRM Systems
* HR Systems
* Vendor Records

## Interested Parties

* Fans
* Employees
* Vendors
* Executive Management
* Regulatory Authorities

## Exclusions

The following are outside the scope of this assessment:

* Football Operations
* Coaching Systems
* Player Performance Analytics
* Stadium Maintenance Systems

Document Owner

Information Security Manager (Case Study)

